#### Artists with the most single certifications

The single, once a humble vinyl disc, now a digital stream, has its own pantheon of champions.

**Most Platinum**

For male artists, [Drake](/Drake_(musician)) stands as the artist with the most Platinum singles, a testament to his prolific output and consistent chart presence.
Among female artists, [Beyoncé](/Beyonc%C3%A9) claims the title for the most Platinum singles, a true queen of the charts.
